{"tid":362120,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點同隻貓減肥","createTime":"2017-08-16T16:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T06:01:40.000Z","uid":74004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c719beadc6c756d20924fcf57a1f31b06ee48d1","tid":362120,"uid":74004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"7歲仔英短 <br />\n食緊減肥糧都由5.1kg升到6.1kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61a41bfbef2fa538c88f45326578f9c7756f1bd","tid":362120,"uid":17530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"多啲同佢玩<br />\n唔好放長糧 <br />\n最好一粒一粒咁餵 <br />\n等佢行下 郁下"},{"pid":"7c7cdbf62c8eaffc2bbf26a10e50ce1f2de20268","tid":362120,"uid":74004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多啲同佢玩<br />\n唔好放長糧 <br />\n最好一粒一粒咁餵 <br />\n等佢行下 郁下</blockquote><br />\n係咪應該放條糧路俾佢一路行一路食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340e28da67c1e18a9e02ad7cbec6eb3086713d2d","tid":362120,"uid":124901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"英短藍貓  因為仲發育緊所以食好多  食完自己兜貓糧又去食狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都好擔心佢過重  但佢日日俾隻狗追  應該可以消耗返  佢真係食好多呀媽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841f5bf5989adc35f4d5146f695cbd5e99626cd5","tid":362120,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"減肥糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高碳水化合物 唔肥就假喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cf15c479e0a7ed389edcd5269417188d1d9df3","tid":362120,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20160327/19544942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20160327%2F19544942&d=oyVdW22Ec2pRcy0RXyv8xW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a6f996f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20160327%2F19544942&h=62234bd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20160327/19544942</a><br />\n減肥糧唔係d咩好野黎<br />\n依個方法唔得就試下轉其他方法<br />\n食乾糧唔夠飽肚就食多d 本身熱量又高其實都幾本末倒置<br />\n試下轉罐頭（主食罐）加多d水 再留意下個卡路里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6123300300bac9dec48f68b0f3ad17b5e1b4a2ee","tid":362120,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"6.1kg都唔係好肥姐<br />\n我屋企3隻後生仲肥 個肚可以用黎拖地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地愈黎愈老 就開始縮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c02130480f4cc5bd27ec95e8e2adb71f063e40","tid":362120,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6.1kg都唔係好肥姐<br />\n我屋企3隻後生仲肥 個肚可以用黎拖地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地愈黎愈老 就開始縮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你比咪佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻糧應該好差下<br />\n老貓縮水因為吸收唔夠蛋白質所以會分解體內肌肉嚟達到消化蛋白質個量"},{"pid":"eb1a9a76fc3571840f7ac7f4bf868b9f97b06505","tid":362120,"uid":128873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:37:19.000Z","msg":"平時每餐減3份1 份量， 肚餓唔洗理佢， 餓一陣唔會死的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de3306c4d60fb600981367e1aad71d1bec62e83","tid":362120,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6.1kg都唔係好肥姐<br />\n我屋企3隻後生仲肥 個肚可以用黎拖地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢地愈黎愈老 就開始縮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你比咪佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻糧應該好差下<br />\n老貓縮水因為吸收唔夠蛋白質所以會分解體內肌肉嚟達到消化蛋白質個量</blockquote><br />\n唔係隻糧差 係佢地'為食'<br />\n海鮮 雞翼雞脾 貓零食 咩都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但年紀大左就食少左 自然就開始瘦<br />\n但3隻都尚算健康 12.15.19歲都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}